{"tid":573471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貨van翻側攔路　出入大潭道交通一度受阻","createTime":"2018-02-26T13:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T13:33:00.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"79d20df675d2d4b6256cd165a9a18dab708c8942","tid":573471,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>大潭道來回方向近民富樓的全線已解封</strong><br />\n<br />\n早上8時27分，一輛客貨車沿大潭道出柴灣，至興民邨民富樓對開，疑跣胎失控，撞上斜坡後再翻跌路中，向左翻側。37歲姓周司機被困車內，要由到場消防員救出，他頭及手受傷送院治理。而一輛駛經的保時捷跑車，疑收掣不及撞向客貨車，60歲保時捷司機未有受傷。受事故影響，目前除巴士及小巴外，其他車輛暫不能由柴灣道轉入大潭道，同時亦不可由石澳道駛入大潭道。運輸署表示，大潭道來回方向近民富樓的全線現已封閉，受影響巴士路線9號及14號須改道行駛。<br />\n<br />\n姓徐的保時捷司機稱，當時他駕車入大潭道遊車河，肇事客貨車車速不高，也沒有轉線，但「突然扭左剷上山坡，一反成架車過咗嚟！」他說慶幸自己已停車，只是被碎片擊中刮花「好好彩呀！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180225/large/1519521197_7577.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180225%2Flarge%2F1519521197_7577.jpg&h=623928f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n客貨車翻側路中。(胡恩宏攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180225/large/1519521251_1950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180225%2Flarge%2F1519521251_1950.jpg&h=2fee072c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保時捷被碎片擊中，司機在場助查。(胡恩宏攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180225/large/1519521614_6fe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180225%2Flarge%2F1519521614_6fe8.jpg&h=6182ccc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受傷司機送院治理。(胡恩宏攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180225/large/1519521686_4dcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180225%2Flarge%2F1519521686_4dcd.jpg&h=82827036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(胡恩宏攝)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180225/57872679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57872679&d=IJnNHdeO5SHS6%2FwiWg0FZXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3cba91c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57872679&h=7759fb55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180225/57872679</a>"}]}